Even when my ears are covered, I hear the heartbeat getting...

00:57:17.250 --> 00:57:19.200
...faster and faster.

00:57:19.200 --> 00:57:25.000
Try to find the right answer, but there's no such thing.

00:57:36.600 --> 00:57:39.300
Hey daddy, tell me... I wonder why those people fight.

00:57:39.300 --> 00:57:41.850
For their name ? For their cash, or for their pride ?

00:57:41.850 --> 00:57:44.400
Those piercingly honest eyes of yours.

00:57:44.400 --> 00:57:47.200
I'm going down. (I'm going down.)

00:57:47.200 --> 00:57:49.500
But everybody's saying, "We're right all the time."

00:57:49.500 --> 00:57:52.300
`cuz they want to stick to absolute justice.

00:57:52.300 --> 00:57:54.800
They're never turning back. Never want to be denied.

00:57:54.800 --> 00:57:58.200
But it's falling down. (It's falling down)

00:57:58.200 --> 00:58:03.400
Patching up the open wounds with the past.

00:58:03.400 --> 00:58:08.650
Remembering the pain that never fades away.

00:58:08.650 --> 00:58:12.650
I draw my blade.

00:58:12.650 --> 00:58:18.650
It's not about becoming a hero to save the world.

00:58:18.650 --> 00:58:23.200
Instead, until my voice wears thin...

00:58:23.200 --> 00:58:33.000
...I want to sing of the future when the crybaby next to me only smiles.

00:58:33.000 --> 00:58:34.650
 I continue to fight.

00:58:34.650 --> 00:58:37.250
Who the fuck do you think you're talking to ? Dumb ass !

00:58:37.250 --> 00:58:39.900
"Don't get carried away," says a snot-nose brat.

00:58:39.900 --> 00:58:42.500
Gutsy, for now, and goes "Should I kick `eem asses?"

00:58:42.500 --> 00:58:45.200
With a faint voice. "Whacha say, huh ?"

00:58:56.650 --> 00:59:04.650
When I close my eyes, I see your tears burnt into mine.

00:59:04.650 --> 00:59:10.050
I swear to myself. I'll never back down.

00:59:11.950 --> 00:59:17.650
It's not about becoming a hero to save the world.

00:59:17.650 --> 00:59:22.500
Instead, until my voice wears thin...

00:59:22.500 --> 00:59:32.900
...I want to sing of the future when the crybaby next to me only smiles.

00:59:32.900 --> 00:59:36.050
Someday, I want our future to be...

00:59:36.050 --> 00:59:43.650
...the place where we can laugh away our tough times.

00:59:43.650 --> 00:59:53.350
In the pouring rain, I long for your heart to be as open as the sunny sky.

00:59:53.350 --> 00:59:55.550
I continue to fight.

